text: An image shared on Facebook purportedly shows an ad released by former Vice President Joe Biden’s campaign that suggests voters should value his heart over his brain.
An image shared on Facebook purportedly shows an Alzheimer’s TODAY magazine cover featuring President Joe Biden.
An image shared on Facebook claims to show President Joe Biden’s face in disgust during a press conference.
A video posted to U.S. President Donald Trump's Facebook page showed Joe Biden's campaign logo superimposed on a coffin.
